  </p>

  <p><strong>Approver: Quilter Financial Services Limited – [APPROVAL DATE TBD]</strong></p>

  <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
  <p>
    The content of this website is provided for general information
    purposes only and does not constitute personal financial advice,
    recommendation or an offer to engage in regulated activity. UK
    Mortgages Worldwide makes every reasonable effort to ensure the
    accuracy and completeness of the information published on this site.
    However, we do not warrant or guarantee that any information is
    accurate, up to date or applicable to your individual circumstances.
  </p>
  <p>
    You should not rely solely on the information provided on this website
    when making financial decisions. Any reliance you place on such
    information is strictly at your own risk. We recommend that you seek
    formal advice from a qualified mortgage adviser before acting on any
