  </p>
  <p>
    Neither UK Mortgages Worldwide, Sandsea Capital Ltd, nor Quilter
    Financial Services Limited accepts any liability for any loss, damage
    or inconvenience arising as a result of the use or inability to use
    this website, or for reliance on its contents, whether arising in
