  </p>
  <p>
    UK Mortgages Worldwide does not accept responsibility for the content,
    availability or security of external websites linked to or from this
    site. The inclusion of any links does not imply endorsement or
    approval of the linked website, its operator, or its content.
  </p>
  <p>
    UK Mortgages Worldwide does not warrant that this site is free from
    errors, viruses or other potentially harmful components. Users should
    ensure they have appropriate cybersecurity protections in place before
